parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and harsh downshifting can cause loss of control, accidents, and damage to the transmission, leading to costly repairs.
symptoms: The transmission slips into gears
harsh downshifting
hesitation when accelerating from downshift mode
manual intervention required to maintain a low gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected opening of the hood while driving can obstruct the driver's view, causing loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The hood unlatches or opens unexpectedly while driving
the hood bends or wraps around the roof of the vehicle
the hood hits the windshield
the hood unlocks by itself when hitting bumps.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the jack can cause the vehicle to fall off the jack, leading to injuries or fatalities, and can also cause damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The jack collapses or breaks while in use
the jack does not hold the vehicle in place
the vehicle falls off the jack.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake proportioning valve can cause uneven brake pressure distribution, leading to reduced stopping power, increased stopping distance, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Spongy brake pedal
uneven brake pedal feel
pulling to one side while braking
increased stopping distance
grinding or screeching noise when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire imbalance and wheel misalignment can cause vibrations in the steering wheel, which can lead to loss of control, reduced traction, and increased risk of tire blowouts, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Constant vibration in the steering wheel
uneven tire wear
pulling or drifting to one side while driving
tire blowouts.
